If you're not sure if you'll like this mix, watch the Avicii video "Wake Me Up" on YouTube or Vevo. It's a crazy mix of genres, like this DVD. Basically, if you don't LOVE music, you probably won't love this mix. 

There's a throwback in there: "Lights" by Ellie Goulding. I don't think I gave that song a fair listen the first time around. Then one day recently it was in my head and I was thinking, who the hell is that? Well I found out and while I still not feeling any of her other popular songs, I concede that "Lights" is a brilliant song and performance. Miley Cyrus still sucks ass.
